8-09-18|archive-date=2018-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180913075638/http://entertainment.time.com/2012/12/13/times-guide-to-the-hobbits-13-dwarves/slide/ori/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使用[[彈弓|彈弓]]作為武器<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://middleearthnews.com/2015/02/19/the-12-days-of-ori-the-full-adam-brown-interview/|title=The 12 Days of Ori – The Full Adam Brown Interview|accessdate=2018-04-30|date=2015-02-19|publisher=Middle-earth News|archive-date=2018-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180501004749/http://middleearthnews.com/2015/02/19/the-12-days-of-ori-the-full-adam-brown-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，穿著用手工編織的淡[[紫色|紫色]]衣服和[[圍巾|圍巾]]，電影美術設計人員表示希望讓歐力的服裝具有「相對柔和、天真的色彩」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://107cine.com/m/mstream/13551/|title=《霍比特人》服装、造型、特效化妆、道具制作，团队创作谈|accessdate=2018-04-30|publisher=影视工业网|archive-date=2019-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190904134015/https://107cine.com/m/mstream/13551/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

